---

**Note**: When creating new documentation, place it in the appropriate subdirectory:
- Workflows and how-tos ‚Üí `guides/`
- Planning and architecture ‚Üí `plans/`
- Results and metrics ‚Üí `reports/`
- Deprecated content ‚Üí `archive/`
